    ClientRequest, Request, RequestIdentifier, Byteable, Summarizable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AcceptPacket

    public class PValuePacket
extends ProposalPacket
    Author:
    arun A three-tuple. The slot and request are within the proposal here. A pvalue is used internally by paxos acceptors and coordinators. It also acts as a DECISION packet as every committed request must be associated with some slot, and ballot.
